      <p>A <a href="ch70s13.html#MonstersO-R102">pseudodragon</a> has a body about 1 foot long, with a 2-foot tail. It weights about 7 pounds.<a href="img/MonstersO-R.Pseudodragon.jpg" target="_blank"><span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="thumb/MonstersO-R.Pseudodragon.jpg" align="right"/></span></a></p>
      <p>A <a href="ch70s13.html#MonstersO-R102">pseudodragon</a> can communicate telepathically and can also vocalize animal noises.</p>
      <div class="sect4" lang="en">
        <div class="titlepage">
          <div>
            <div>
              <h5 class="title"><a name="id2136937"/>Combat</h5>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
          <div class="keyword">monsterinfo</div>
        </div>
        <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersO-R103"/>
        <p>A <a href="ch70s13.html#MonstersO-R102">pseudodragon</a> can deliver a vicious bite, but its principal weapon is its sting-equipped tail.</p>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2136969"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersO-R104"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Poison (Ex):</strong></span> Injury, Fortitude DC 14, initial damage sleep for 1 minute, secondary damage sleep for 1d3 hours. The save DC is Constitution-based and includes a +2 racial bonus.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2136999"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersO-R105"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Blindsense (Ex):</strong></span> A <a href="ch70s13.html#MonstersO-R102">pseudodragon</a> can locate creatures within 60 feet by nonvisual means (mostly hearing and scent, but also by noticing vibration and other environmental clues). Opponents the <a href="ch70s13.html#MonstersO-R102">pseudodragon</a> can't actually see still have total concealment against the <a href="ch70s13.html#MonstersO-R102">pseudodragon</a>.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2137060"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersO-R106"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Telepathy (Su):</strong></span> <a href="ch70s13.html#MonstersO-R102">Pseudodragons</a> can communicate telepathically with creatures that speak Common or Sylvan, provided they are within 60 feet.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2137099"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersO-R107"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Skills:</strong></span> <a href="ch70s13.html#MonstersO-R102">Pseudodragons</a> have a chameleonlike ability that grants them a +4 racial bonus on <a href="ch16s03.html#CombinedSkills179">Hide</a> checks. *In forests or overgrown areas, this bonus improves to +8.</p>
          <p/>
        </div>
